@startuml
title Neighbor-Army_help-with-covid Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Next.js Frontend" as Frontend
participant "Firebase Auth" as Auth
participant "Firebase Functions" as Functions
participant "Onfleet API" as Onfleet
participant "Sendgrid API" as Sendgrid
participant "Google Maps API" as GoogleMaps
participant "Twilio API" as Twilio

User -> Frontend: Access application
Frontend -> Auth: Authenticate user
Auth --> Frontend: Return authentication status

alt Request Help
    User -> Frontend: Fill request form
    Frontend -> GoogleMaps: Autocomplete address
    GoogleMaps --> Frontend: Return address suggestions
    User -> Frontend: Submit request
    Frontend -> Functions: Send help request
    Functions -> Onfleet: Create task
    Onfleet --> Functions: Confirm task creation
    Functions --> Frontend: Confirm request received
    Frontend --> User: Display confirmation
else Offer Help
    User -> Frontend: Fill volunteer form
    Frontend -> GoogleMaps: Autocomplete address
    GoogleMaps --> Frontend: Return address suggestions
    User -> Frontend: Submit volunteer info
    Frontend -> Functions: Send volunteer data
    Functions -> Twilio: Verify phone/zipcode
    Twilio --> Functions: Confirm verification
    Functions -> Onfleet: Create worker
    Onfleet --> Functions: Confirm worker creation
    Functions -> Sendgrid: Add email to mailing list
    Sendgrid --> Functions: Confirm email addition
    Functions --> Frontend: Confirm volunteer registration
    Frontend --> User: Display confirmation
end

@enduml